graph TB
    Start[START] --> Agent[agent 节点<br/>LLM 思考]
    Agent --> Condition{条件判断<br/>should_continue}
    
    Condition -->|有 tool_calls| Tools[tools 节点<br/>执行工具]
    Condition -->|无 tool_calls| End[END<br/>结束]
    
    Tools --> Agent
    
    style Start fill:#81c784
    style End fill:#e57373
    style Agent fill:#64b5f6
    style Tools fill:#ffb74d
    style Condition fill:#ba68c8
